Package: smpic
Type: Package
Title: Creates Images Sized for Social Media
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mikkel Freltoft Krogsholm
Maintainer: Mikkel Freltoft Krogsholm <mikkel@56n.dk>
Description: Creates images that are the proper size for social media.
        Beautiful plots, charts and graphs wither and die if they are
        not shared. Social media is perfect for this but every platform
        has its own image dimensions. With 'smpic' you can easily save
        your plots with the exact dimensions needed for the different
        platforms.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
